#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:987
msgid "The Sampler section can be **hidden** in the :ref:`Mixxx user interface <interface-overview>`. Click the :ref:`SAMPLER <interface-expansion-buttons>` button, or use the specific :ref:`appendix-shortcuts` to show or hide the section."
