#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1144
msgid "Preview Deck Section"
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1156
msgid "The Preview Deck with a track loaded"
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1158
msgid "The Preview Deck is a special deck that allows you to pre-listen to tracks in the headphones before using them in your mix. Pre-listening a track does not change the tracks's :guilabel:`Played` state as well as the play counter and is not logged in the :ref:`History <library-history>`. Press :kbd:`CTRL` + :kbd:`4` (Windows/Linux) or :kbd:`CMD` + :kbd:`4` (Mac) to display the Preview Deck."
